Subject: [PATCH 3/5] Replace MessageLoopimpl with libuv for lynx bts

Delegate the MessageLoopimpl of LynxJS threads to libuv.
On PC, run both NodeJS and Lynx BTS message loops within the same libuv event loop to unify and optimize event handling.

issue: m-6796469046
